node.text: This month on #PrimarkSpotlight, we meet the incredibly talented singer/songwriter @iamkyami. Kyami chats to us about finding empowerment within her true sound and pushing through failures to find successes. On a chilled Friday vibe? Make sure you go and check out 'IAmKyami' on Spotfiy for the ultimate soundtrack to match your mood ✨ #Primark #FeelGoodFriday

node.text: Did you know that we’ve partnered with The Ellen MacArthur Foundation? The EMF promotes the idea of a circular economy in order to tackle some of the biggest challenges of our time, such as plastic pollution, climate change, and biodiversity loss. Increasingly built on renewable materials, and underpinned by a shift to renewable energy, a circular economy is distributed, diverse, and inclusive. This means that this denim 👆is designed, produced and created to meet the guidelines of The Ellen MacArthur Foundation's Jean Redesign project, to make fashion circular. Jeans made using organic cotton £19/€21/$24 #PrimarkCares
